                                “Long-Term Political and Economic Framework,” nor a revision of it,
                                was among the annexes accompanying <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                                    >NSC</gloss> 68/3, the annexes to which received National
                                Security Council and Presidential approval on December 14.</p>
